Package: cartilage
Title: Spatializing 'rayshader' 
Version: 0.0.0.9001
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Michael",
           family = "Sumner",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "mdsumner@gmail.com")
Description: Drive rayshader's image creation within a geospatial context. Input a spatial object
 (i.e. a raster) and build a record of the input object, the ray-shaded product along with a
 3D plot as a side-effect. This simplifies the integration of rayshader products with more 
 general tasks. 
